  "detailed_description": "<strong>Wood 'n Stones is an innovative rogue-lite survival game set in the Stone Age, where cooperation between the player and the other NPCs is the key to the final victory.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/4870fb6f32d3c819b9c8b603257d1fe6.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>While dinosaurs and other evil creatures pose a danger to the future of humankind, you can be the leader who will allow our species to survive to the present day, thanks to the help of a great friend, a puppy, and all the people that you'll save during the journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/be9908ea05983cbd0532478027083316.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>You can gather Wood and Stones to help out your tribe defending yourself and them, and build campfires to protect your way better. But beware: <strong>the weather can change at any time</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/47101bc385c294f98b07981eff57420b.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Wood 'n Stones is an innovative rogue-lite survival game set in the Stone Age, where cooperation between the player and the other NPCs is the key to the final victory.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/4870fb6f32d3c819b9c8b603257d1fe6.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>While dinosaurs and other evil creatures pose a danger to the future of humankind, you can be the leader who will allow our species to survive to the present day, thanks to the help of a great friend, a puppy, and all the people that you'll save during the journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/be9908ea05983cbd0532478027083316.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>You can gather Wood and Stones to help out your tribe defending yourself and them, and build campfires to protect your way better. But beware: <strong>the weather can change at any time</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118470/extras/47101bc385c294f98b07981eff57420b.avif?t=1658520850\" width=600 height=80 /></span>",
